{"tid":1372754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣組 民陣入］元朗後請立即籌備8月5日全港大罷工","createTime":"2019-07-27T13:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T01:57:59.000Z","uid":27203,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fbcd2608b11d3407ed23d1dc8a542d08b459ca99","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"［死線升級］8月4號大遊行 5號全港大罷工升級<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364469</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n上次有兩千幾個正評 希望今次大家真係付諸實行 係自己個行組織罷工<br />\n<br />\n8月4日前 文宣呼籲公司 市民 公務員參與 <br />\n同政府講8月4日夜晚六點係死線<br />\n<br />\n8月4日<br />\n民陣大遊行（可合併 港島遊行）規模要69 616級數<br />\n<br />\n8月5日 大罷工 集會 以及升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實際時間地點可以待定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n<br />\n醫護人員：維持有限度及緊急服務 非緊急醫療職系就罷工啦唔該<br />\n<br />\n地鐵：因為要留後路比義士 所以市區線維持服務 但係機場線可以考慮罷駛 <br />\n<br />\n地面交通司機：係指定時間後 大家記得唔好係隧道同主要幹道死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n航空界：罷工令機場停擺<br />\n<br />\n其他紀律報隊：罷工出黎/穿制服出黎保護市民<br />\n<br />\n記者：做番自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n私人公司 同 公務員： AO EO個啲唔該罷工出黎<br />\n<br />\n出唔到黎既同我戴口罩頭盔穿黑衫番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知大家會驚冇左份工<br />\n但係有啲人冇埋命 自由 同前途 <br />\n如果連呢啲都做唔到 香港根本唔配有民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：8月5號見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咪阻我搵食<br />\n<br />\n幫推頂置熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為自由而戰</span></span>"},{"pid":"f97bb340f0bc885adec7f05fb41fd1dac6262e3a","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:37:37.000Z","msg":"10連"},{"pid":"94b236364be2d5c8aab18a3439e7f1e235d4eaba","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:37:47.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1c0eb35496cbc531bb447812cb9151253fb859a3","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"c85e089cbfd69844c69e315f53ac46ac2071fc57","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"dd9551e084abd1a5a890d9cca31f8d97e1e416b6","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"0b81df1ece0209714c1510e328cd3253c3c9bce7","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:38:27.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"bded3405503b7cc1f7ce0db33d23d2ea5dce493a","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6b7aa0cc4500b3a564a49853349e93713af7860d","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:38:49.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f7596878f2aa71425b4abe9eedbecc39af3f7ecb","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8ff9c281123c8d85328923dc7b938c2047738c51","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7763212f715780d7d24ea5c396708befe6ee3821","tid":1372754,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:39:21.000Z","msg":"20連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a618a9369cd85da8f26b0e1be8aa6846721c340","tid":137275